name: Classic Paneer Butter Masala
description: Rich, creamy North Indian curry made with paneer, tomatoes, and aromatic spices.
ingredients: ["200g paneer cubes","2 tomatoes","1 onion","1 tbsp butter","Cream","Spices"]
steps: ["Sauté onions and tomatoes.","Blend to a smooth paste.","Cook paste with spices.","Add paneer and simmer.","Finish with cream and butter."]

name: Garlic Butter Pasta
description: Simple yet delicious pasta tossed with garlic, butter, and herbs.
ingredients: ["200g pasta","3 garlic cloves","2 tbsp butter","Olive oil","Mixed herbs"]
steps: ["Boil pasta until al dente.","Sauté garlic in butter.","Add herbs.","Mix pasta with sauce.","Serve hot."]

name: Chicken Tikka Wrap
description: Spicy and juicy chicken tikka wrapped in a soft roti with veggies.
steps: ["Marinate chicken in spices.","Grill until cooked.","Warm rotis.","Add veggies and chicken.","Roll and serve."]

name: Veg Fried Rice
description: Chinese-style fried rice with lots of veggies and soy sauce.
steps: ["Heat wok with oil.","Add chopped veggies.","Add rice and mix.","Pour soy sauce.","Stir-fry for 2 minutes."]

name: Butter Garlic Prawns
description: Juicy prawns tossed in butter, garlic, and herbs.
steps: ["Clean prawns.","Sauté garlic in butter.","Add prawns.","Cook for 5 minutes.","Finish with lemon juice."]

name: Cheese Corn Sandwich
description: Creamy, cheesy sandwich stuffed with corn and spices.
steps: ["Mix corn with cheese.","Spread on bread.","Grill with butter.","Cut and serve."]

name: Egg Curry Masala
description: Spicy and flavorful boiled-egg curry cooked in a tomato-onion masala.
steps: ["Prepare masala.","Add boiled eggs.","Cook until thick.","Garnish with coriander."]

name: Veggie Omelette (No Egg!)
description: A chickpea-flour-based eggless omelette full of veggies.
steps: ["Mix all ingredients.","Heat pan with oil.","Pour batter.","Flip after golden.","Serve hot."]

name: Chocolate Mug Cake
description: A quick, fluffy, microwave chocolate cake made in a mug.
steps: ["Mix everything in a mug.","Microwave for 1 minute.","Let it cool.","Enjoy!"]
